-- Buffett: Chosen successor does not know it
-- 
-- Mon Feb 27, 2012 6:54am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/02/27/us-buffett-successor-idUSTRE81Q0ZX20120227

 

 (Reuters) - Warren Buffett's chosen successor as chief executive officer of Berkshire Hathaway ( BRKa.N ) does not know he has been chosen for the role, Buffett told CNBC on Monday. 
 The board has a name in mind and has had for years now, Buffett said Monday. (Reporting by  Ben Berkowitz  in Boston; Editing by Lisa Von Ahn)